For each of the {= sector_band =} sector bands listed below, cover {= production_case =}+ Russian production cases and each of the {= evidence_facet =} evidence facets listed below. For every production case / evidence facet combination, supply {= url =}+ public URL that gives page-specific evidence for that case and facet.

A production case is a named producer together with a concrete product, product line, facility project, material capability, or production project. The producer alone is too broad, and a product name without a producer is too ambiguous.

